description: This is a short quiz that will tell you what you should eat based on your responses to a series of questions. At the end of the quiz, when Alexa presents your ideal food, you can say "tell me more" to hear a description, "yes" to start over, or "no" to end the game.
exampleInteractions: Alexa open what should i eat
name: What Should I Eat
shortDescription: A short quiz that will tell you what you should eat based on preference
